###
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/LogisticsService/Vehicles

###1. Available Vehicles
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Vehicles?$filter=status eq 'Available'

###2. Shipments In Transit
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$filter=status eq 'InTransit'

###
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "3867c3a7-c09b-48f6-a84c-2f33010ab882",
  "trackingNumber": "SL-2026-00003",
  "customer_ID": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "driver_ID": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
  "vehicle_ID": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333",
  "pickupAddress": "Gorakhpur Warehouse",
  "deliveryAddress": "Lucknow Hub",
  "pickupCity": "Gorakhpur",
  "deliveryCity": "Lucknow",
  "weight": 75,
  "status": "Booked",
  "bookedAt": "2026-05-31T10:00:00Z",
  "paymentStatus": "Pending"
}

###3. Shipments for Customer
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$filter=customer_ID eq '11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111'
### 4. Update Shipment Status to In Transit
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "77777777-7777-7777-7777-777777777777",
  "trackingNumber": "SL-2026-00009",
  "customer_ID": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "driver_ID": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
  "vehicle_ID": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333",
  "pickupAddress": "Lucknow Warehouse",
  "deliveryAddress": "Kanpur Hub",
  "pickupCity": "Lucknow",
  "deliveryCity": "Kanpur",
  "weight": 120
}

###5. Mark Shipment Delivered
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments(77777777-7777-7777-7777-777777777777)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Delivered",
  "deliveredAt": "2026-05-31T12:00:00Z"
}

###6. Routes Between Cities
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Routes?$filter=fromCity eq 'Kanpur' and toCity eq 'Lucknow'

###7. Drivers by Rating
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Drivers?$orderby=rating desc